 al-Bah\u0323r\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37990,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/19\/bidah-replace-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33240,"position":4},"title":"Hassan on Bid\u2019ah: Every religious innovation replaces a Sunnah like it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Awza\u2019i reported: Hassan ibn \u2018Atiyyah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cNo people fabricate an innovation in their religion but that Allah will remove a Sunnah from like it, then it will never come back to them until the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 99 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36940,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/14\/sufism-quran-sunnah-fiqh\/","url_meta":{"origin":33240,"position":5},"title":"Junayd on Tasawwuf: True Sufism based on Quran, Sunnah, and Fiqh","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 14, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Hasan \u2018Ali reported: Al-Junayd ibn Muhammad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cOur knowledge of Tasawwuf is defined by the Book and the Sunnah. Whoever does not memorize the Quran, nor write the prophetic teachings, nor study their understanding, he is not to be followed in it.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars